      • isConstraintViolated

        public boolean isConstraintViolated(VenueTime venueTime)
        The method loops through each panel panelists and for each it takes the unique days the panelists appears in and then it counts the number of panels within the specified time difference between one panel and the next one in each of these days. Doing that will count if the panelists is showing up for consecutive panels in a day.

        Returns:
